oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Chris Brown at the Sommet Center
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Concert tours; Woodcuts (prints); skylines
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (gold and silver on white) announcing Chris Brown and Bow Wow with Soulja Boy, Sean Kingston, and Lil Mama on the Up Close and Personal Holiday Exclusive Tour appearing at the Bridgestone Arena (formerly the Sommet Center) on January 10. Poster features a woodcut of the Nashville skyline.
